1
00:00:00,490 --> 00:00:02,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who are <i>you</i> supposed to be?</font>

2
00:00:02,110 --> 00:00:03,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">His name is Namu-san.</font>

3
00:00:03,730 --> 00:00:10,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's a great psychic whose powers are 
so strong, he can't settle in one place.</font>

4
00:00:10,490 --> 00:00:14,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your powers don't work 
on normal human beings.</font>

5
00:00:14,600 --> 00:00:19,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is exactly why monsters 
can't live among humans.</font>

6
00:00:31,890 --> 00:00:33,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Impact"><font size="50">Kaya-chan Isn't Scary</font></font></font>

7
00:00:31,890 --> 00:00:33,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Impact"><font size="50">Kaya-chan Isn't Scary</font></font></font>

8
00:00:32,770 --> 00:00:36,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Impact"><font size="50">Kaya-chan Isn't Scary</font></font></font>

9
00:01:51,380 --> 00:01:55,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><b>{\an3}<font color="#ffffff">Episode 9: People Who Can See Them Aren't Scary?</font></b></font></font>

10
00:01:52,350 --> 00:01:57,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}My parents abandoned me
 for being different.</i></font>

11
00:01:57,890 --> 00:02:01,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is Namu-kun. 
He'll be joining us from today.</font>

12
00:02:01,820 --> 00:02:03,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's all help him feel welcome.</font>

13
00:02:04,220 --> 00:02:06,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nice to meet you, Namu-kun. 
My name is—</font>

14
00:02:06,440 --> 00:02:07,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Momoko.</font>

15
00:02:09,120 --> 00:02:12,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's what the person hanging
 behind you is calling you.</font>

16
00:02:11,580 --> 00:02:18,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Momoko. Momoko.</font>

17
00:02:13,710 --> 00:02:16,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're hanging onto your shoulders. 
You must feel the weight.</font>

18
00:02:17,070 --> 00:02:18,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll get rid of it for you.</font>

19
00:02:21,140 --> 00:02:22,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's super weird.</font>

20
00:02:22,230 --> 00:02:23,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}He's a freak.</font>

21
00:02:23,440 --> 00:02:24,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe he's got a screw loose?</font>

22
00:02:24,020 --> 00:02:26,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}This is why his parents left him.</font>

23
00:02:33,340 --> 00:02:37,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial Black">{\an3}<font size="18"><font color="#252526">Punishment Room</font></font></font></font>

24
00:02:33,340 --> 00:02:35,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Being around everyone was exhausting,</i></font>

25
00:02:35,960 --> 00:02:39,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>so the punishment room was perfect 
for me, since I could be alone there.</i></font>

26
00:02:39,310 --> 00:02:41,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Georgia"><font color="#141313">I won't say mean things
\h\h\h\hto my friends anymore.</font></font></font>

27
00:02:43,730 --> 00:02:46,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#c2bfbf">m 0 0 l 100 0 100 100 0 100</font></font>

28
00:02:43,730 --> 00:02:46,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia"><b>{\an7}<font color="#252725">I truly regret what I did, and hope I can
 make up with my friends. I understand this 
is home to others who each have their own...</font></b></font></font>

29
00:02:47,310 --> 00:02:49,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an7}<font color="#b1b1b2">m 0 0 l 100 0 100 100 0 100</font></font>

30
00:02:47,310 --> 00:02:49,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia"><font size="13">{\an7}<font color="#0b0b0c">I feel profound remorse when looking back on who I was until yesterday.
I understand that my actions and words caused distress and harm to others
at the facility, and I deeply regret that. Moving forward, I am determined
to make a fresh start and become a better person.

First, I would like to sincerely apologize for repeatedly making careless 
remarks towards my friends who live at the same care facility, and for 
causing them harm as a result. I regret allowing my own anxiety and painful 
experience turn into anger in my words. Moving forward, I want to focus on 
respecting others' feelings and building relationships where we understand 
one another.

I further express my deep remorse for repeatedly behaving and speaking 
in ways that caused fear among the staff and fellow residents. They are here 
to support us and deserve our respect. Going forward, I will remember this, 
work cooperatively, and make an effort to build a safe and mutually 
supportive environment.

I fully acknowledge that my past actions resulted in my isolation from those
 around me. From now on, I will actively engage in communication, cooperate 
with others, and strive to create a community filled with mutual support 
and smiles. I sincerely pledge to become someone who brings positive 
influence to others through my words and actions, and who treats everyone 
with respect. I am truly sorry for</font></font></font></font>

31
00:02:49,820 --> 00:02:53,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia">{\an8}<font size="50"><font color="#080808">truly
sorry
for</font></font></font></font>

32
00:02:51,720 --> 00:02:55,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>People are unforgiving of things
 they don't understand.</i></font>

33
00:02:53,900 --> 00:02:56,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Don't mess with me! The heck is your problem?</font>

34
00:02:57,160 --> 00:03:01,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They ran every evaluation on me
 and had me on all kinds of medications.</i></font>

35
00:03:15,460 --> 00:03:17,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, you mean <i>that</i> rumor?</font>

36
00:03:17,090 --> 00:03:20,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Room 313, was it? The room upstairs?</font>

37
00:03:20,690 --> 00:03:23,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, precisely. Do you happen 
to know anything about it?</font>

38
00:03:23,600 --> 00:03:27,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They say patients who get 
put in there attempt suicide.</font>

39
00:03:28,850 --> 00:03:31,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Word is, they smash their heads
 against the wall.</font>

40
00:03:31,940 --> 00:03:35,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. I'd love to hear the details—</font>

41
00:03:35,430 --> 00:03:37,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Behind you! Look behind you!</font>

42
00:03:37,060 --> 00:03:37,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

43
00:03:43,730 --> 00:03:46,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? I'm still alive?</font>

44
00:03:46,760 --> 00:03:51,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, you're awake, huh? 
You're lucky those bushes broke your fall.</font>

45
00:03:52,270 --> 00:03:53,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who are you?</font>

46
00:03:53,330 --> 00:03:56,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My apologies. 
This should answer your question.</font>

47
00:03:58,180 --> 00:04:00,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A "psychic"?</font>

48
00:04:00,440 --> 00:04:05,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yup. I've been investigating the rumor 
that an evil spirit haunts this room.</font>

49
00:04:05,300 --> 00:04:09,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's when I encountered you, just as you
 were about to become its next victim.</font>

50
00:04:11,600 --> 00:04:18,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You got lucky this time, but it will 
happen again if you stay in this room.</font>

51
00:04:18,110 --> 00:04:24,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But never fear! I, the psychic
Mob Osamu, will protect you, Namu-san.</font>

52
00:04:24,800 --> 00:04:25,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eek!</font>

53
00:04:24,960 --> 00:04:27,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Excuse me! Don't go entering places
 without permission!</font>

54
00:04:27,860 --> 00:04:28,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get him out of here.</font>

55
00:04:29,220 --> 00:04:30,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}On it.</font>

56
00:04:29,440 --> 00:04:33,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">W-W-W-Wait! Hold up! Wait a minute!</font>

57
00:04:30,360 --> 00:04:31,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Let's go, pal.</font>

58
00:04:33,130 --> 00:04:36,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's the victim of an unknown threat!</font>

59
00:04:37,590 --> 00:04:39,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What was that man's problem?</font>

60
00:04:39,520 --> 00:04:42,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's just loopy, that one.</font>

61
00:04:43,820 --> 00:04:45,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's right.</i></font>

62
00:04:45,640 --> 00:04:49,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>People would just call me crazy 
if I talked about what I see.</i></font>

63
00:04:49,950 --> 00:04:53,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And he thought I tried to kill myself
 because I was possessed?</i></font>

64
00:04:53,400 --> 00:04:55,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Not even close.</i></font>

65
00:04:56,030 --> 00:04:59,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Still, calling it a fall 
is pretty pathetic, too.</i></font>

66
00:04:59,850 --> 00:05:03,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But I guess no one would care 
either way if I lived or died.</i></font>

67
00:05:03,660 --> 00:05:07,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't even care myself.</i></font>

68
00:05:07,410 --> 00:05:12,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I, the psychic Mob Osamu, 
will protect you, Namu-san.</font>

69
00:05:15,770 --> 00:05:17,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Nobody asked you to.</i></font>

70
00:05:20,220 --> 00:05:23,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Listen carefully. 
This is a protective talisman.</font>

71
00:05:21,130 --> 00:05:23,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b>{\an8}<font face="Georgia"><font size="70"><font color="#232321">Execute
at once</font></font></font></b></font>

72
00:05:23,220 --> 00:05:26,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Put this and some salt 
at each corner of the bed. Plop!</font>

73
00:05:23,220 --> 00:05:28,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b>{\an8}<font face="Georgia"><font size="20"><font color="#232321">Execute
at once</font></font></font></b></font>

74
00:05:23,220 --> 00:05:28,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b>{\an8}<font face="Georgia"><font size="20"><font color="#232321">Execute
at once</font></font></font></b></font>

75
00:05:23,220 --> 00:05:28,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b>{\an8}<font face="Georgia"><font size="20"><font color="#232321">Execute
at once</font></font></font></b></font>

76
00:05:23,220 --> 00:05:28,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b>{\an8}<font face="Georgia"><font size="20"><font color="#232321">Execute
at once</font></font></font></b></font>

77
00:05:26,270 --> 00:05:28,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At the very least, 
this area will be protected.</font>

78
00:05:28,970 --> 00:05:34,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">However! If the salt loses its shape, 
discolors, or gathers dust,</font>

79
00:05:34,220 --> 00:05:38,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it'll have the opposite effect.
 If that happens, replace it with fresh—</font>

80
00:05:37,300 --> 00:05:38,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Hey, mister.</font>

81
00:05:38,840 --> 00:05:39,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes?</font>

82
00:05:39,940 --> 00:05:43,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone's making fun of you. 
Doesn't that bother you?</font>

83
00:05:43,880 --> 00:05:46,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good grief. Listen to yourself.</font>

84
00:05:47,310 --> 00:05:50,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We all perceive the world 
in slightly different ways.</font>

85
00:05:50,780 --> 00:05:53,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When that gap becomes too vast,</font>

86
00:05:53,440 --> 00:05:58,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it's natural for people to feel uneasy
 or want to deny what's being said.</font>

87
00:05:58,500 --> 00:06:03,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's no one's fault, and it's not
 something I need to feel ashamed about.</font>

88
00:06:03,600 --> 00:06:06,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's a pretty self-serving way
 to look at it.</font>

89
00:06:09,180 --> 00:06:13,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And yet, Namu-san, you're not 
rejecting my presence. Why is that?</font>

90
00:06:14,830 --> 00:06:16,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No reason.</font>

91
00:06:16,620 --> 00:06:18,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm just killing time.</font>

92
00:06:18,940 --> 00:06:22,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You <i>again</i>? How do you keep getting in?</font>

93
00:06:20,390 --> 00:06:26,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}H-How? Well, um, that is to say, uh...</font>

94
00:06:22,670 --> 00:06:26,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get out! I'm seriously
 gonna call the cops!</font>

95
00:06:26,200 --> 00:06:27,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stay strong!</font>

96
00:06:27,950 --> 00:06:30,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I promise I'll protect you—</font>

97
00:06:28,590 --> 00:06:31,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Come on now. You've babbled long enough.</font>

98
00:06:31,810 --> 00:06:33,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}You're pretty strong, aren't you?</font>

99
00:06:34,890 --> 00:06:38,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>"We all perceive the world 
in slightly different ways."</i></font>

100
00:06:39,490 --> 00:06:45,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Up until he said that, I thought I was 
the only one who saw a different world.</i></font>

101
00:06:45,510 --> 00:06:48,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b>{\an8}<font face="Georgia"><font size="26"><font color="#232321">Execute
\hat once</font></font></font></b></font>

102
00:06:48,310 --> 00:06:51,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are these? They're totally fake.</font>

103
00:06:54,390 --> 00:06:57,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Still, we should avoid this 
turning into a long battle.</i></font>

104
00:06:57,270 --> 00:06:59,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Let's do a stakeout and wrap it up fast.</i></font>

105
00:07:01,640 --> 00:07:04,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The plan is simple and straightforward.</i></font>

106
00:07:10,060 --> 00:07:12,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll be on standby in the room next door.</i></font>

107
00:07:12,420 --> 00:07:16,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If anything happens, he'll knock 
to signal me, and I'll charge in.</i></font>

108
00:07:16,500 --> 00:07:19,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Then, with my homemade
 exorcism spray...</i></font>

109
00:07:21,430 --> 00:07:23,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Time to put my skills to work!</i></font>

110
00:07:27,260 --> 00:07:29,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font size="16">{\an8}<font color="#22262c">Purify</font></font></b></font></font>

111
00:07:41,270 --> 00:07:43,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sh-Shame on me!</font>

112
00:07:44,530 --> 00:07:47,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you doing, mister?</font>

113
00:07:48,810 --> 00:07:51,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Namu-san! 
Th-Thank goodness you're all right!</font>

114
00:07:50,550 --> 00:07:52,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}This isn't what we agreed on.</font>

115
00:07:52,330 --> 00:07:53,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm terribly sorry!</font>

116
00:07:53,670 --> 00:07:58,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I promised I'd come immediately when 
I heard a knock on the wall. So I'm very—</font>

117
00:07:56,650 --> 00:07:58,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Yeah, so...</font>

118
00:07:58,450 --> 00:08:00,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why were <i>you</i> banging on the wall?</font>

119
00:08:00,580 --> 00:08:03,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Uh, no.</font>

120
00:08:04,060 --> 00:08:06,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I didn't...</font>

121
00:08:20,130 --> 00:08:22,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">N-Namu-san, what room is this?</font>

122
00:08:22,900 --> 00:08:23,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

123
00:08:25,570 --> 00:08:28,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Room 313.</font>

124
00:08:28,070 --> 00:08:30,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Oh, you mean </i>that<i> rumor?</i></font>

125
00:08:30,030 --> 00:08:32,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Room 313, was it?</i></font>

126
00:08:32,580 --> 00:08:36,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They say patients who get 
put in there attempt suicide.</i></font>

127
00:08:36,630 --> 00:08:39,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Word is, they smash their heads
 against the wall.</i></font>

128
00:08:53,030 --> 00:08:55,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mister, what do you see?</font>

129
00:08:57,340 --> 00:08:59,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">E-Everything's going to be okay.</font>

130
00:08:59,600 --> 00:09:05,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I'm a p-p-psy... 
I'm a psychic here to protect you.</font>

131
00:09:09,530 --> 00:09:11,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Namu-san, run—</font>

132
00:09:18,110 --> 00:09:19,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mister?</font>

133
00:09:27,250 --> 00:09:32,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What made me think I could 
take on something like this?</font>

134
00:09:32,540 --> 00:09:34,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">H-Help me!</font>

135
00:09:35,820 --> 00:09:39,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, Namu-san! This room is dangerous!
You have to leave at once!</font>

136
00:10:09,170 --> 00:10:11,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks for looking after me.</font>

137
00:10:12,220 --> 00:10:15,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, no, don't mention it!</font>

138
00:10:15,300 --> 00:10:20,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But for a so-called psychic, 
you suck at dealing with ghosts, mister.</font>

139
00:10:21,030 --> 00:10:22,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So...</font>

140
00:10:22,750 --> 00:10:26,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Starting today, I'm your master 
and you'll be my student.</font>

141
00:10:29,510 --> 00:10:32,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Got it, Osamu-kun?</font>

142
00:10:33,610 --> 00:10:37,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><b>{\an3}<font color="#ffffff">Chie-sensei Isn't Scary</font></b></font></font>

143
00:10:40,220 --> 00:10:46,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can't just sit back while my student 
gets involved in something so dangerous.</i></font>

144
00:10:46,570 --> 00:10:49,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kaya-chan!</font>

145
00:10:47,320 --> 00:10:48,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Kaya!</font>

146
00:10:49,320 --> 00:10:52,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry. It's because 
I took my eyes off her.</font>

147
00:10:52,700 --> 00:10:55,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, it's my fault for 
stopping you to chat.</font>

148
00:10:55,890 --> 00:10:57,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll look over there.</font>

149
00:10:57,840 --> 00:10:59,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll check that side.</font>

150
00:11:08,730 --> 00:11:11,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>H-He's...</i></font>

151
00:11:16,710 --> 00:11:17,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop!</font>

152
00:11:20,410 --> 00:11:25,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're N-Namu-san, right? 
Where are you taking Kaya-chan?</font>

153
00:11:25,150 --> 00:11:27,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm pretty strong, you know.</font>

154
00:11:27,260 --> 00:11:29,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's awfully rich.</font>

155
00:11:29,770 --> 00:11:32,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're the one who left <i>this</i> in the crowd.</font>

156
00:11:36,090 --> 00:11:39,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What were you gonna do 
if someone saw her like this?</font>

157
00:11:39,590 --> 00:11:44,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess she's never run into a problem 
she couldn't fix with brute force.</font>

158
00:11:44,140 --> 00:11:47,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She doesn't even know 
how to retract her claws.</font>

159
00:11:47,550 --> 00:11:50,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Figures. She's a monster 
that's barely hatched.</font>

160
00:11:50,500 --> 00:11:51,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kaya-chan!</font>

161
00:11:53,570 --> 00:11:56,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's okay. I'm right here with you.</font>

162
00:11:56,920 --> 00:12:00,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't have to be afraid. 
Let's go back to your daddy, okay?</font>

163
00:12:00,570 --> 00:12:03,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's okay. You're safe.</font>

164
00:12:05,220 --> 00:12:08,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's with that "I'll protect you,
no matter what" attitude of yours?</font>

165
00:12:08,760 --> 00:12:10,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you obsessed with it?</font>

166
00:12:10,730 --> 00:12:14,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or is that how you tame it?</font>

167
00:12:15,530 --> 00:12:17,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Quite impressive, Sensei.</font>

168
00:12:17,760 --> 00:12:19,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cut it out already!</font>

169
00:12:19,540 --> 00:12:23,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Barely hatched"? "Tame"? 
She's not an animal.</font>

170
00:12:23,070 --> 00:12:27,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Besides, aren't you also 
a psychic yourself?</font>

171
00:12:27,040 --> 00:12:30,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I don't know about that.</font>

172
00:12:30,580 --> 00:12:31,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

173
00:12:31,520 --> 00:12:38,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sensei, did you honestly believe 
everything that child said from the start?</font>

174
00:12:39,150 --> 00:12:45,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you hadn't seen "them" yourself, 
how would you have treated her?</font>

175
00:12:46,170 --> 00:12:47,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There you go saying "No" again.</font>

176
00:12:47,920 --> 00:12:50,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can't just say "No" to everything.</font>

177
00:12:50,920 --> 00:12:54,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When someone deviates 
too far from the norm,</font>

178
00:12:54,790 --> 00:12:57,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">they're marked as defective 
and cast aside.</font>

179
00:12:58,280 --> 00:13:02,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They then get slapped with 
a plausible label like "psychic."</font>

180
00:13:03,300 --> 00:13:05,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But even deviation has degrees.</font>

181
00:13:05,900 --> 00:13:07,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It exists on a spectrum.</font>

182
00:13:07,810 --> 00:13:12,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And when it tips too far, 
you're practically dealing with a beast.</font>

183
00:13:13,520 --> 00:13:19,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even I find it hard to 
recognize her as a fellow human.</font>

184
00:13:19,210 --> 00:13:22,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Osamu-kun worships her like she's divine,</font>

185
00:13:22,060 --> 00:13:25,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but nothing born into that family 
could ever be so benevolent.</font>

186
00:13:26,420 --> 00:13:29,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's something far more
 malevolent instead.</font>

187
00:13:29,910 --> 00:13:31,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you mean?</font>

188
00:13:32,350 --> 00:13:35,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And how would <i>you</i> know that?</font>

189
00:13:35,750 --> 00:13:36,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because...</font>

190
00:13:37,770 --> 00:13:41,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm Ebisumori Namu, I guess.</font>

191
00:13:42,340 --> 00:13:43,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ebisumori?</font>

192
00:13:43,750 --> 00:13:45,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tell me, Sensei.</font>

193
00:13:45,630 --> 00:13:48,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That thing you're holding so dearly...</font>

194
00:13:48,460 --> 00:13:52,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you sure it's what 
you believe it to be?</font>

195
00:13:53,260 --> 00:13:54,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you doing?!</font>

196
00:13:54,410 --> 00:13:56,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Watch closely, Sensei.</font>

197
00:13:57,220 --> 00:14:01,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is what a woman from 
the Ebisumori family <i>really</i> is.</font>

198
00:14:09,540 --> 00:14:14,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is what's inside Sato Kaya.</font>

199
00:14:17,040 --> 00:14:22,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="30"><font face="Arial"><b><font color="#e76092">Kaya-chan
<font size="22">\h\h\hIsn't</font></font></b></font></font></font>

200
00:14:17,040 --> 00:14:22,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="30"><font face="Arial"><b><font color="#e76092">Scary</font></b></font></font></font>

201
00:14:32,450 --> 00:14:34,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kaya-chan, stay with me.</font>

202
00:14:34,300 --> 00:14:35,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kaya-chan!</font>

203
00:14:36,960 --> 00:14:38,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What did you do to her?</font>

204
00:14:38,980 --> 00:14:41,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you talking to?</font>

205
00:14:41,270 --> 00:14:43,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This</i> is Sato Kaya.</font>

206
00:14:43,490 --> 00:14:44,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

207
00:14:44,620 --> 00:14:47,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The thing you call "Kaya-chan"</font>

208
00:14:47,120 --> 00:14:51,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">is a specter from the Ebisumori family 
wrapped in human skin.</font>

209
00:14:51,750 --> 00:14:54,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For generations, Ebisumori's eldest 
daughter, the shrine maiden,</font>

210
00:14:54,800 --> 00:14:57,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">has carried a power beyond the ordinary.</font>

211
00:14:57,360 --> 00:15:00,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">While its intensity varies, 
the power manifests</font>

212
00:15:00,420 --> 00:15:03,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">when the shrine maiden's
 inner self is replaced by a specter.</font>

213
00:15:04,160 --> 00:15:09,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I can see the change. 
That's why I know.</font>

214
00:15:09,640 --> 00:15:13,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The "inner self" of that thing 
has been completely replaced.</font>

215
00:15:13,470 --> 00:15:16,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's not a trace of 
the human element left.</font>

216
00:15:17,100 --> 00:15:20,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For generations, the family has claimed 
this aberrant power as its own,</font>

217
00:15:20,460 --> 00:15:23,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">discarding whatever doesn't suit them.</font>

218
00:15:24,070 --> 00:15:27,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And in the end, they have become
 specters themselves, it seems.</font>

219
00:15:28,320 --> 00:15:34,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><b><font size="10"><font color="#4f504e">Hasumi Chie</font></font></b></font></font>

220
00:15:28,650 --> 00:15:33,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I couldn't care less if they self-destructed,
dragging the entire family down.</font>

221
00:15:33,610 --> 00:15:37,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The problem is Osamu-kun is totally
enthralled with this thing, just like you.</font>

222
00:15:34,330 --> 00:15:38,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="35"><font color="#202224">She's so amazing</font></font></b></font>

223
00:15:34,330 --> 00:15:38,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="35"><font color="#202224">I can't contain myself</font></font></b></font>

224
00:15:34,330 --> 00:15:38,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="35"><font color="#202225">Kaya-sama is supreme</font></font></b></font>

225
00:15:38,330 --> 00:15:43,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And to protect his life, 
I will exorcise this specter.</font>

226
00:15:44,020 --> 00:15:49,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you get it now? The "Sato Kaya" 
you're trying to protect...</font>

227
00:15:52,400 --> 00:15:54,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">never existed in the first place.</font>

228
00:15:55,360 --> 00:15:57,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're a victim of this, too, Sensei.</font>

229
00:15:58,440 --> 00:16:01,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've been through a lot 
of scary things, haven't you?</font>

230
00:16:01,980 --> 00:16:07,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll take care of it. If you need the 
body, go ahead and take it.</font>

231
00:16:07,320 --> 00:16:11,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Although having her listed as "missing" 
is probably the easiest option—</font>

232
00:16:20,390 --> 00:16:22,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you out of your mind?</font>

233
00:16:23,140 --> 00:16:24,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take it back.</font>

234
00:16:24,440 --> 00:16:25,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

235
00:16:26,190 --> 00:16:27,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take it back!</font>

236
00:16:28,760 --> 00:16:30,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kaya-chan's not human?</font>

237
00:16:31,140 --> 00:16:33,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't know anything about her!</font>

238
00:16:34,250 --> 00:16:35,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kaya-chan is...</font>

239
00:16:36,240 --> 00:16:37,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's...</font>

240
00:16:40,210 --> 00:16:41,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't want to change.</font>

241
00:16:42,400 --> 00:16:45,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you can't eat lunch
 in those dirty clothes.</font>

242
00:16:45,530 --> 00:16:46,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fine, I won't.</font>

243
00:16:46,690 --> 00:16:48,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, come on. Please?</font>

244
00:16:48,690 --> 00:16:52,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's in total stickler mode. 
She's not gonna bend.</font>

245
00:16:52,040 --> 00:16:54,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's been doing so well lately.</font>

246
00:16:54,830 --> 00:16:56,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a mess.</font>

247
00:16:56,540 --> 00:16:57,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shush.</font>

248
00:16:59,830 --> 00:17:02,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At least tell me why 
you don't want to change.</font>

249
00:17:03,050 --> 00:17:04,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wouldn't understand.</font>

250
00:17:04,350 --> 00:17:05,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

251
00:17:06,000 --> 00:17:08,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not like you'd understand anyway!</font>

252
00:17:08,830 --> 00:17:09,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

253
00:17:16,440 --> 00:17:17,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kaya-chan.</font>

254
00:17:19,140 --> 00:17:20,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Chie-sensei?</font>

255
00:17:20,550 --> 00:17:22,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I did some thinking.</font>

256
00:17:22,620 --> 00:17:27,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Could it be you don't want to change 
because you <i>really</i> like that outfit?</font>

257
00:17:27,780 --> 00:17:29,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Wrong.</font>

258
00:17:29,750 --> 00:17:31,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then, are you shy about getting changed?</font>

259
00:17:31,770 --> 00:17:32,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nope.</font>

260
00:17:32,700 --> 00:17:35,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're just in the mood 
to stay muddy all day?</font>

261
00:17:35,130 --> 00:17:36,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's not it at all.</font>

262
00:17:36,600 --> 00:17:38,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not?</font>

263
00:17:39,110 --> 00:17:41,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are you asking me?</font>

264
00:17:47,580 --> 00:17:50,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because I want to get 
to understand you, Kaya-chan.</font>

265
00:17:52,430 --> 00:17:54,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I wasn't even close, huh?</font>

266
00:17:56,390 --> 00:17:57,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sensei...</font>

267
00:17:59,520 --> 00:18:03,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't hate me?</font>

268
00:18:03,510 --> 00:18:09,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why would I? I love you 
so much, Kaya-chan.</font>

269
00:18:16,220 --> 00:18:17,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Long sleeves.</font>

270
00:18:19,730 --> 00:18:22,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wanna wear long sleeves. Because...</font>

271
00:18:24,120 --> 00:18:25,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I turn black.</font>

272
00:18:26,820 --> 00:18:31,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But the other teacher 
said I was being selfish.</font>

273
00:18:31,420 --> 00:18:33,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't know what she meant.</font>

274
00:18:33,640 --> 00:18:36,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But as long as I could feel
 her inner struggle,</font>

275
00:18:36,280 --> 00:18:38,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the meaning of her words didn't matter.</font>

276
00:18:39,220 --> 00:18:43,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You probably don't understand because 
you only pay attention to the surface.</font>

277
00:18:43,930 --> 00:18:45,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So what if she's a specter inside?</font>

278
00:18:46,310 --> 00:18:49,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No matter what you say, 
it doesn't change the fact</font>

279
00:18:49,690 --> 00:18:53,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that Kaya-chan gets angry, struggles, 
feels joy, and laughs, like anyone else.</font>

280
00:18:54,450 --> 00:18:58,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She has a human heart.</font>

281
00:18:59,040 --> 00:19:03,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And if you're still going to treat her 
like a monster, I'll make you pay.</font>

282
00:19:04,330 --> 00:19:06,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll protect Kaya-chan, no matter what!</font>

283
00:19:08,080 --> 00:19:11,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll be the one who 
protects you, Kaya-chan.</font>

284
00:19:17,110 --> 00:19:18,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? What's happening?</font>

285
00:19:29,610 --> 00:19:31,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tch. It got too close to the body.</font>

286
00:19:31,190 --> 00:19:33,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After I finally managed to separate it...</font>

287
00:19:34,140 --> 00:19:35,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can I pull it off again?</font>

288
00:19:38,550 --> 00:19:39,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is...</font>

289
00:19:49,230 --> 00:19:51,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Chie-sensei.</font>

290
00:19:51,420 --> 00:19:54,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kaya-chan! It's you, right, Kaya-chan?</font>

291
00:19:56,200 --> 00:19:57,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I...</font>

292
00:19:59,070 --> 00:20:00,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I...</font>

293
00:20:09,350 --> 00:20:11,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I got lost!</font>

294
00:20:15,000 --> 00:20:18,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You must've been scared 
all by yourself. You're safe now.</font>

295
00:20:19,570 --> 00:20:22,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go find your daddy together, okay?</font>

296
00:20:24,160 --> 00:20:25,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Daddy!</font>

297
00:20:25,380 --> 00:20:26,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kaya!</font>

298
00:20:26,490 --> 00:20:29,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry for all the trouble. 
Thank you for finding her.</font>

299
00:20:29,140 --> 00:20:31,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not at all. I'm glad she's all right.</font>

300
00:20:31,580 --> 00:20:33,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bye-bye, Chie-sensei.</font>

301
00:20:33,880 --> 00:20:35,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you very much.</font>

302
00:20:36,070 --> 00:20:37,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bye-bye.</font>

303
00:20:38,930 --> 00:20:42,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't tell me you're still trying 
to do something to Kaya-chan.</font>

304
00:20:42,110 --> 00:20:44,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not. Or more like, I can't.</font>

305
00:20:45,850 --> 00:20:49,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can only deal 
with spiritual things.</font>

306
00:20:49,510 --> 00:20:52,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can intervene if the specter's
out of control and fully manifested.</font>

307
00:20:53,030 --> 00:20:56,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I can't do anything
if it's contained within a vessel.</font>

308
00:20:57,110 --> 00:21:01,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How did you put it back inside? 
Are you in that line of work?</font>

309
00:21:01,030 --> 00:21:02,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course not.</font>

310
00:21:02,710 --> 00:21:07,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Something must have made her 
genuinely want to return to this world.</font>

311
00:21:08,910 --> 00:21:11,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll protect Kaya-chan, no matter what!</font>

312
00:21:11,450 --> 00:21:16,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I, the psychic Mob Osamu, 
will protect you, Namu-san.</font>

313
00:21:17,900 --> 00:21:21,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That sounds just like 
a normal human being.</i></font>

314
00:21:26,430 --> 00:21:31,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It looks like I need to do 
a little more research.</i></font>

315
00:21:45,370 --> 00:21:50,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an9}<b><font size="10">Translation
Timing
Editing
Quality Control
Translation Check</font></b></font>

316
00:21:45,370 --> 00:21:50,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an7}<b><font size="10">Naomi Suda
Krzysztof Kunc
SMR
Gabriella Alabanza
Rei Miyasaka</font></b></font>

317
00:23:10,030 --> 00:23:40,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="12">{\an8}<font color="#c3587e">Kaya-chan Isn't Scary</font></font></b></font>

318
00:23:11,380 --> 00:23:15,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The reason Kaya-chan's skin turns black 
when she defeats a specter</i></font>

319
00:23:15,300 --> 00:23:19,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>is because what's inside her pierces 
through her skin and becomes visible.</i></font>

320
00:23:20,940 --> 00:23:24,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She doesn't understand why it happens,</i></font>

321
00:23:24,560 --> 00:23:27,620
